result.name: 漁牧 Fisher & Farmer

reviews.text:
Hidden on the top floor of Mega Box, Fisher & Farmer is a Chinese restaurant that serves Sichuan cuisine, hotpot and chicken pot. To our surprise, the interior design is quite modern and nice.

But, these real edible pigs displayed at the entrance were a bit scary…

We ordered a Seabass in Sour and Spicy Style with add-on Sweet Potato Noodle in the bottom. We adored the taste so much! As sour fish pots are usually made with pickles, but this one was made with lime, which was so refreshing and not overly sour. Very enjoyable! The portion of seabass was much larger than we expected. The two of us just managed to finish the three big pieces of seabass in the pot.

Sweet potato noodle was definitely a good add-on to go for, as it soaked up the soup and was so flavored. It was also great to go with the fish.

We also ordered a chicken cartilage as an appetizer. Yet, it was served later than the fish pot. Nevertheless, it was quite delicious with its numbing spicy flavor.
This is a great place, excellent interiors design , the cost is reasonable and the most important is you don't need to quene for a long time in Sunday!

It was great to download the app and redem the dinner coupon.
Overall taste are similar to other branches , seating more comfortable .
delicious place

reviews.text:
Yesterday we had our first Chinese New Year family gathering at the place. The dishes were way too salty. 

The dish "Boston lobster with noodles" was disappointing... the entire Boston lobster was presented in three quarter only on the dish. When we reflected our disappointment to one of the manager, he was impolite and defensive. 

As we paid our bill, before signing the credit card slip we bother to take a look and there's one charged snack item which never showed up on the table. As we pointed out the mistake, the manager didn't even bother to explain why this situation happened ? 

Would I recommend this place to other... the answer is a NO!
We have team lunch here nearly every month. They have a big table which can fit like 16 people. Food is above average, service is great
Good yum cha

reviews.text: 招呼、環境不錯，點心幾好食，早去飲茶幾舒服。
地方寬敞光猛，坐得舒適，服務人員態度很好，食物質素一流，款式種類繁多吸引，每個位置都可看到電視，附近很多購物商店，飯後也不愁沒有好去處！
景观唔错,食物水平都几好,九龙湾有免费巴士接驳,交通都算方便
點心種類太小，味道又不太好，有選擇不會再去

reviews.text:
坐位好窄，我地6位俾4人卡位我地坐。
食物偏咸，沒有免費清水，礦泉水盛惠$15支。

簡單啲講

張檯有咁窄得咁窄，張凳有咁迫得咁迫咪等d友坐得咁舒服，食完拿拿聲好走，

支飲管有咁粗得咁粗，冰有咁大舊放咁大舊，杯汽水咪chur一聲飲完買過第二杯囉
買相太差，表示師傅完全不專重食材和客人感受，所以不會再去

好‘很’難食！
唯一可讚只係地方闊！坐得舒服

麻辣烤海鱸魚
完全無麻，食辣野一定要重味！但又唔夠味，條魚一係死左好耐一係就炸定淋汁，完全唔係滑既，又‘鞋’口又硬既D肉，翻炸或者係炸完擺係到好耐先會有咁既情況！仲有一個情況就係炸到過左時，但睇條魚無收絲就唔似 （因為我自己都做左好多年廚房，分得出）

Cocktail
成杯酒無酒味！應該係漏左落酒，可惜唔係我飲，我只係試最後個啖！ 咁既蜜瓜水就收65蚊！

口水雞
呢個叫做好D，但都係偏咸！

食到一半搵下呢間係咩集團，原來係太興！
唔怪得有呢D水準，如果早d知道係太興，就唔會幫襯！

非常美味的中式菜，烹調很用心，最普通的菜式也煮出高水準，回味無窮！
特別推薦酸菜水煮魚和北京烤鴨，其他的也很好吃！
此餐廳適合家庭、朋友、或商業上的飯聚，裝修設計典雅，座位寬敞舒適，車子停泊在Mega Box 14樓停車場 🅿️ 步行來此餐廳吃飯，非常方便。

Hidden on the top floor of Mega Box, Fisher & Farmer is a Chinese restaurant that serves Sichuan cuisine, hotpot and chicken pot. To our surprise, the interior design is quite modern and nice.

But, these real edible pigs displayed at the entrance were a bit scary…

We ordered a Seabass in Sour and Spicy Style with add-on Sweet Potato Noodle in the bottom. We adored the taste so much! As sour fish pots are usually made with pickles, but this one was made with lime, which was so refreshing and not overly sour. Very enjoyable! The portion of seabass was much larger than we expected. The two of us just managed to finish the three big pieces of seabass in the pot.

Sweet potato noodle was definitely a good add-on to go for, as it soaked up the soup and was so flavored. It was also great to go with the fish.

We also ordered a chicken cartilage as an appetizer. Yet, it was served later than the fish pot. Nevertheless, it was quite delicious with its numbing spicy flavor.
